{"tid":1952182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍於香港墜機","createTime":"2020-03-31T12:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T14:23:14.000Z","uid":306513,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bae110947165e065737e683101f68751db84c9cb","tid":1952182,"uid":306513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:30:03.000Z","msg":"保安局發言人今日表示，保安局於今日收到中國人民解放軍駐香港部隊（駐軍）的知會，得悉3月30日下午，駐軍一架直升機在大欖郊野公園一帶執行飛行訓練任務時失事。事故並未涉及任何民居受損或市民受傷，駐軍會根據駐軍法處理及調查事件，保安局會繼續與駐軍了解事件。不過新聞稿中未有提及事件中是否有駐港解放軍傷亡。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3Nprrh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3Nprrh.jpg&h=68381f59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09a13107abfe6dfebf5a95a95a961b5f5190b18b","tid":1952182,"uid":84102,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c38695583a174d6e72687c458b012b44756ca2d","tid":1952182,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09a13107abfe6dfebf5a95a95a961b5f5190b18b","tid":1952182,"uid":84102,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"臨墜機影"},{"pid":"54f8a69ccf15d498a2787c4f7a0ace985dd6d21c","tid":1952182,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:32:48.000Z","msg":"蘋果又加1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075cb904b189a523eec78421ec7c5099d0f7ff49","tid":1952182,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"打飛機打得勁得滯"},{"pid":"3a6325e4fa8d1c940fe6d7e48c33514754fdaab2","tid":1952182,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:33:55.000Z","msg":"幅配圖 神來之筆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/